Toolbar

5 main Components

Play|Pause|Step Through

Play: CTRL + P : Game View
Pause: CTRL + SHIFT + P : Scene View
Step Through: Helps with Debugging


Layers: Groups Objects. If Layer of GameObject was selected in Inspector...you will have access to Layers in Toolbar section

Layouts: Duplicate of Windows -> Layouts

Transform Tools: Hand tool, Move tool, Rotation tool, Scale tool and 2D transform -> which changes UI

Pivot: Transform Gizmo Toggles -> rotates or scales depending on the position of the pivot point.

Global|Local: Global = global axes/ Local = inherits Parent's rotation/transform

Account: signing in

Service: online/offline


